title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 363-3.2 - End use

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 363-3.2 - End use

State Regulations

The owner or operator of a disposal facility where an end
use is proposed must meet the requirements of section
363-9.7. Notes
